Nimirum in foliolo sphin- rosporifero observavi venas istas infra apicem fere reticulatim conjunctas, et intra areas his ambientibus formatas, sphaerosporas singulas aut paucas inclusas. In planta admodum tenera venas conferre ad partes continendas facilius quis conjiceret. Cellulas carpostomium ambi- entes in Keramidio globoso fere prominentes esse, quoque hoe loco addere placet.
